#. type: Plain text
#: HandBook.adoc:753
#
msgid "To choose which services start at boot: servicesetup and gtkservicesetup."
msgstr "起動時に開始するサービスを選択するには: servicesetup と gtkservicesetup"

#. type: Plain text
#: HandBook.adoc:754
#
